            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Nova international has immense potential to redefine education. Spread across a vast campus, the school offers a thoughtfully designed infrastructure that promises to meet the needs of modern education. The passionate founders bring a clear vision and dedication to creating a nurturing environment for students, focusing on holistic development and academic excellence. A promising choice for parents seeking a forward-thinking school for their children!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Nova International School - Wakad"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Vicky Patil"
          },
          "datePublished": "2025-01-11",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Exceptional Education at Nova International School\n\nNova International School is truly a beacon of excellence in education. The institution stands out for its commitment to fostering a holistic learning environment where students excel academically, socially, and emotionally.\n\nThe faculty are not only highly qualified but also incredibly dedicated and nurturing. They take a personalized approach to teaching, ensuring that each child reaches their fullest potential. The school's emphasis on critical thinking, creativity, and problem-solving equips students with essential life skills that go beyond textbooks.\n\nNova’s state-of-the-art facilities and diverse extracurricular programs create a balanced environment where children can explore their interests and talents. The integration of technology and innovative teaching methods makes learning engaging and future-oriented.\n\nThe school's focus on values, cultural awareness, and global citizenship is truly commendable. It prepares students to thrive in a multicultural and interconnected world while instilling in them a strong sense of responsibility and empathy.\n\nNova International School is more than just a school—it’s a community where every child is valued and encouraged to shine. I wholeheartedly recommend it to any parent looking for a transformative educational experience for their child.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
